title: Grateful Dead Live at Alpine Valley Music Theatre on 1989-07-19
description: Set 1 Hell In A Bucket, Sugaree, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, Althea, Victim Or The Crime-> West L.A. Fadeaway, Desolation Row-> Deal Set 2 Box Of Rain-> Foolish Heart-> Looks Like Rain, Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> The Wheel-> Morning Dew, E: Turn On Your Love Light material from this show is featured in the video Downhill from Here

reviews.review_text:
A generous helping. Thank you so much mr. Baker for providing this find audience recording of one of my favorite venues.  I unfortunately didn't make it to this particular run, several of my friends did, they had one word for the show, mud. Oh and yeah they said it was all probably one of the best shows that they've ever seen.
    Setlist is killer,  boys all seem to be in perfect form.
    Kindness from Duluth, man, Baker. I'm sure I know you from early 9os, from MN kind folk... ☮ Thx again!
 ...Jimmy
